snippet.title: GameBoy - Pokémon FireRed and LeafGreen Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a remake of Japan's Pokémon Red and Green (known as Red and Blue overseas). Battle your friends, collect new Pokémon, and discover untold secrets! Gotta catch 'em all!

http://www.pokemon.com/us/
SUBSCRIBE AND RATE!!
